## Overview
An empty CSS file serving as the Compass placeholder for print media styles. Contains only the standard Compass welcome comment and a `/*# sourceMappingURL=print.css.map */` reference. No print-specific styles have been defined. This is the `app/assets/css/` location counterpart to `app/styles/print.css`.

## Interface
No exports. Empty placeholder stylesheet.

## Dependencies
No project-level dependencies.

## Implementation Notes
- 5 lines — Compass welcome comment + source map reference
- Generated by the Yeoman Angular generator Compass scaffold
- No print styles have been authored for the TuyoTools frontend
- Counterpart: `app/styles/print.css` (also empty, without source map reference)
